| Type        = Soundtrack
| Artist      = [[Vishal Bhardwaj]]
| Cover       = Kaminey_Album.jpg
| Border      = yes
| Alt         = The poster showing a man in a club, with pinkish red themed colour in the background
| Caption     = Soundtrack cover
| Released    = 6 July 2009
| Recorded    = 2008
| Genre       = [[Film soundtrack|Feature film soundtrack]]
| Length      = {{Duration|m=35|s=57}}
| Language    = [[Hindi language|Hindi]]
| Label       = [[T-Series]]
| Producer    = Hitesh Sonik, [[Clinton Cerejo]]
| Last album  = ''[[Haal-e-dil]]''<br />(2008)
| This album  = '''''Kaminey'''''<br />(2009)
| Next album  = ''[[Ishqiya]]'' <br/>(2010)
